steps.name: Login With valid credentials
Click Workflow and click Receiving
Enter "SAMPLE-10" into Barcode search criteria and click Find button
Double-click search result
Click Search criteria and enter "SAMPLE-11" into Barcode search criteria and click Find button
Double-click search result again
Click OK button on the Find Assets to Receive screen
Click Department elipsis button and select "Quality Department"
Enter "Test_Location" and enter "3" and enter "Test_Contact"
Select "Mechanical" for Work Area
Select "One Time Only" for Reason for Service
Select "In Tolerance" for Initial Condition
Check On Site checkbox and check Expedite checkbox
Select second asset and verify the Department is blank
Verify Location is blank
Verify Work Area is "Electronic"
Verify Reason of Service is "Normal Cycle"
Verify Initial Condition is blank
Verify Quantity is "1" and Contact Info is blank
Verify On Site checkbox is unchecked
